                            </supportDesc>
                            <layoutDesc>
                                <layout columns="1" writtenLines="25 28">
                                    <p>Written in one column. It would appear that even in their
                                        original state the pages did not all contain the same number
                                        of lines. Fol. 1r, where no complete line is missing, has 28
                                        lines; fol. 1v has 27 and the trace of a 28th. Fol. 2r has
                                        26 lines but is possibly defective at the top, while no
                                        lines are missing from fol. 2v, which have 25 lines plus the
                                        conclusion of a word which was begun at the bottom line.</p>
                                </layout>
                            </layoutDesc>
