                                    century</date> (<bibl>
                                    <ref type="secondary-1" target="KKKat">KKKat</ref>
                                </bibl>).</p>
                        </origin>
                        <acquisition>
                            <p>According to the AM-slip, Árni Magnússon bought the
                                fragment on <name type="person" key="OddSig001">Oddur
                                    Sigursson's</name> auction in <name type="place" key="Copen01">Copenhagen</name>
                                <date when="1727">1727</date>. Back then it was used as binding material for a printed book in
                                12mo: <q xml:lang="is">Var utanum prentada bok in 12mo ä Oddz
                                    Sigurdz sonar auction i Kaupenhafn. 1727.</q>
                            </p>
